cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper presents an end-to-end radar odometry system for autonomous driving, which falls under the scope of robotics.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The system uses a correlation-based radar matching approach, which involves image processing techniques and falls under the scope of computer vision.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The system is trained in a (self-)supervised way using only previously obtained pose information as a training signal, which involves machine learning techniques.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The system uses machine learning techniques to improve the accuracy of radar odometry, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents a system for autonomous driving, which involves control systems and falls under the scope of systems and control.
